{"lastModified":1772813845045,"uri":"c::16875063630::vessel::d5cc78d7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Australia\n\nRhemtide is a 76-foot luxury motor yacht, featuring spacious front, upper, and aft decks designed for all leisure and entertainment needs. Built with classic elegance, she is the perfect yacht for hosting intimate cruises, private parties, or corporate events, accommodating up to 46 guests.\n\nThe main deck offers a wide, user-friendly area complete with a full-size bar and lounge space, ideal for entertaining guests. On the bow, relax in luxury with custom seating or soak up the sun on the sunbeds, or opt for the expansive sundeck with an inflatable waterslide for extra fun.\n\nRhemtide blends comfort and craftsmanship, with sophisticated interiors that highlight the natural beauty of the yacht. Large windows throughout the yacht provide exceptional light penetration, creating a bright and airy atmosphere on both the main deck and guest cabins.\n\nThe vessel boasts three elegant cabins for up to six guests, each with an ensuite bathroom. The main deck features a welcoming saloon where guests can relax and entertain in complete comfort.\n\nRhemtide is the ultimate companion for your day on the water, offering luxury, style, and unforgettable experiences.","blueprint":{"name":"RHEMTIDE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc78d7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7f16a290-6d4b-11f0-920b-a3b920cad32b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc78d7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3dbbd4a0-6d4b-11f0-ae2a-df7f80690d7b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc78d7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3dbb3860-6d4b-11f0-ae2a-df7f80690d7b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc78d7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3dc21630-6d4b-11f0-983f-a57427fb67e0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc78d7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3df18aa0-6d4b